Module passwordmanager
Package passwordmanager.model

Class EntryBuilder

java.lang.Object
passwordmanager.model.EntryBuilder
public class EntryBuilder extends Object
Builder class for creating Entry instances. This class follows the Builder pattern to facilitate the construction of Entry objects.
